Use the `getCookies()` method from the `HttpServletRequest` object. This returns an array of `Cookie` objects. You must then loop through this array to find the specific cookie you need.
Example:
`Cookie[] cookies = request.getCookies();
if (cookies != null) {
    for (Cookie cookie : cookies) {
        if (cookie.getName().equals("key")) {
            String value = cookie.getValue();
        }
    }
}`
